{"tid":2040622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[移民/BNO/BC即係點？] 重温1989年港台「悲哀的香港人」","createTime":"2020-05-28T16:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T05:06:20.000Z","uid":123696,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"329a6d7e0015b988f9b7300d6f632c54b409fff4","tid":2040622,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZLyc2VSgw-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZLyc2VSgw-Q&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=bf10d082\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZLyc2VSgw-Q</a><br />\n<br />\n條片講1989年香港人點樣移民去美國、澳洲、加拿大。<br />\n同埋點樣爭取英國畀香港人BC，而唔係BNO。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等大家喺思考點樣移民嘅過程中借古鑑今。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有兩點想大家記住：<br />\n1. BC係英國嘅道義責任，當年無畀BC，係現任執政黨（保守黨）嘅錯。而戴卓爾同賀維嘅錯，應該由同為保守黨嘅莊漢生糾正，而唔係只用另類居英權計劃（例如降低門檻）敷衍港人。之後等嗰啲走唔到嘅怪自己無能力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 無錯，而家主導權喺英政府度，首先好多謝Hong Kong Watch等團體嘅游說工作，我亦都知要一步一步去做，而唔係獅子開大口。不過，我哋一定要記住，講到底BC係entitlement，所以終極目標係BNO轉BC，而且可by descent繼承一代。唔可以再好似30年前咁，自己受惠於居英權計劃就放棄其他香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講開又講：建議港台拍2020版「悲哀的香港人」<br />\n想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c107d51c9907abb5d3031ae05cc49a2e52b4d193","tid":2040622,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329a6d7e0015b988f9b7300d6f632c54b409fff4","tid":2040622,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZLyc2VSgw-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZLyc2VSgw-Q&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=bf10d082\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZLyc2VSgw-Q</a><br />\n<br />\n條片講1989年香港人點樣移民去美國、澳洲、加拿大。<br />\n同埋點樣爭取英國畀香港人BC，而唔係BNO。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />